CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 16, 1945, pg. 22, reads: "Birthday Celebrants - Little Billie Jean Boston recently celebrated her fourth birthday, at the home of Mrs. Mary Clark, 3039 Centre Avenue. Present at the gay celebration were Marie Smith, Marjorie Smith, Jacqueline Maynard, Norman Taylor, Ruth Jones, Jewel Hairston and Tylene Howard. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marie Smith, Marjorie Smith, Jacqueline Maynard, Norman Taylor, Ruth Jones, Jewel Hairston and Tylene Howard gathered around Billie Jean Boston blowing out candles on cake for her fourth birthday party in home of Mary Clark, 3039 Centre Avenue, Hill District
